    # "You recoil. He jumps."
    "당신은 뒷걸음질 치고, 그는 펄쩍 뜁니다."

# game/story/2_rejection_of_relationship.rpy:66
translate korean rejection_of_relationship_1397610e:

    # ICARUS "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA!"
    ICARUS "으아아아아아아아아아!"

